Lindberg, 1955; from pond 3 to Laguna Montebello, Chiapas. A First urosomite, and genital double-somite, ventral B Urosome, ventral C Anal somite and caudal ramus, ventral D Urosome, ventral E Anal somite and caudal ramus, ventral. Scale bars 50 
